WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:47.877
Did you see it?

00:00:47.877 --> 00:00:50.333
It's neat looking.

00:00:53.055 --> 00:00:54.327
We see if it makes it fall.

00:01:02.239 --> 00:01:04.106
Well, good evening, family.

00:01:04.106 --> 00:01:05.291
Praise the Lord.

00:01:05.291 --> 00:01:07.119
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:01:07.119 --> 00:01:09.020
We're excited to be here tonight.

00:01:09.020 --> 00:01:11.119
I have some things on my heart.

00:01:11.119 --> 00:01:12.520
Well, we did it.

00:01:12.520 --> 00:01:14.827
Thank you for the 600,000 subscribers.

00:01:14.827 --> 00:01:20.719
To those that have subscribed, isn't it amazing what Jesus did?

00:01:21.546 --> 00:01:32.229
Even if it goes back to the fives for a little bit, because sometimes it fluctuates a lot after I do a live stream because a lot of people get ticked off at what I say, or if they like it, they stay; if they don't, they leave.

00:01:32.229 --> 00:01:34.423
But we're there.

00:01:34.423 --> 00:01:39.839
And isn't it amazing what the Lord has done in just two and a half years?

00:01:39.839 --> 00:01:46.919
We set out to do this prayer channel and do it all to the glory of God.

00:01:46.919 --> 00:01:51.000
All we say in word and in deed, we give all to the glory of God.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:53.920
And it's pretty amazing watching.

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:58.000
See if people start leaving; watch.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:58.592
Isn't that neat?

00:01:58.592 --> 00:02:00.664
I don't want to look at it.

00:02:00.664 --> 00:02:02.240
We went through it though.

00:02:04.126 --> 00:02:05.269
Regardless, we saw it.

00:02:05.269 --> 00:02:06.530
It's like having a touchdown.

00:02:06.530 --> 00:02:13.088
You can say we still made a touchdown even if they try to call it back.

00:02:13.088 --> 00:02:14.311
But you know what?

00:02:14.311 --> 00:02:16.239
It's all to the glory of God.

00:02:16.239 --> 00:02:20.159
It's neat to watch it as we grow.

00:02:20.159 --> 00:02:31.022
We are 400,000 away from what the Lord said our goal was: to set out for and to believe God for a million-man and woman prayer army.

00:02:31.022 --> 00:02:34.720
And you know, there's a lot there.

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:35.543
Isn't it amazing?

00:02:36.091 --> 00:02:53.888
Most people would say, 'Well, you know, that was an overnight success,' and I say no, that's taken a lot of cultivation, an acceleration of walking with Him.

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:56.959
Let's go ahead and get to the news.

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:09.480
Now, I'm a little bummed for what I saw in the spirit and what manifested today.

00:03:09.480 --> 00:03:17.960
I didn't release this publicly until right now: what I saw in the spirit about the woman FED.

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:22.159
Now, I saw this woman right here.

00:03:22.364 --> 00:03:27.200
I never made her public—who I saw—but I told you all, 'I see a woman, and I'm praying over this woman.

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:44.160
' I knew in the valley of decision that Trump was making this week that this was a major decision concerning whatever the Lord had us praying over, right?

00:03:44.160 --> 00:03:56.640
He said the decisions he will make this week, going into the third, will be the fork in the road.

00:03:56.640 --> 00:04:01.920
And I saw this woman right here.

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:04.959
Do you see her?

00:04:05.306 --> 00:04:12.319
I didn't know that she was even able to run and be a part of the Fed, but this is the woman I saw.

00:04:12.319 --> 00:04:18.840
And Braden said, 'Daddy, this is who I believe Trump is looking at.

00:04:18.840 --> 00:04:22.880
' Now, she didn't make it.

00:04:22.880 --> 00:04:25.832
Is that a good thing or a bad thing?

00:04:25.832 --> 00:04:27.840
I don't know.

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:30.328
I haven't got to pray it out enough.

00:04:30.328 --> 00:04:35.200
But in the valley of decision, he picked somebody that was very hawkish.

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:49.088
He picked this man today.

00:04:49.088 --> 00:04:58.390
Do you see who he picked today?

00:04:58.400 --> 00:04:59.872
This guy.

00:04:59.872 --> 00:05:02.080
He picked him.

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:07.728
And does it matter what I feel?

00:05:07.728 --> 00:05:15.919
I mean, I have my opinion of what I feel in my spirit, of what I'm praying over, and does the Senate approve it?

00:05:15.919 --> 00:05:20.140
Because they have to approve it now and the things go before the Senate.

00:05:20.140 --> 00:05:29.840
But in my spirit, I have been praying over this since October, very strongly.

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:35.150
And the major valley—isn't it amazing the Lord would give us even this week?

00:05:35.150 --> 00:05:44.240
He said he'll make major decisions that will make or break his term concerning the next couple of weeks going into the third.

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:50.462
This is January 30th and 31st; the third is next week.

00:05:50.462 --> 00:05:58.080
And everything the Lord said—these are major decisions concerning Iran, concerning Israel.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:05:59.679
How will we handle Israel?

00:05:59.679 --> 00:06:02.520
How will he handle Gaza?

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:15.956
How will he handle liberating the Iranian people from a regime that is tyrannical, that is killing young people like nothing?

00:06:15.956 --> 00:06:25.479
It's like I talked to Donné Clement and Patricia, and we were talking about it.

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:39.759
It's like a Holocaust for all the bodies and all the things that are not being exposed and shown for what they are doing to their people; it's like a genocide.

00:06:39.759 --> 00:06:43.440
And we pray for the Iranian people.

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:44.040
We do.

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:52.765
I pray for the Christians, the underground church of Iran in Iran, and that we would see a major revival.

00:06:53.336 --> 00:06:59.079
Remember, the Lord has shown us so many times that He was bringing liberation; He was bringing a major revival.

00:06:59.079 --> 00:07:10.048
And as I was sitting and I was praying even early this morning, the Lord said, 'It takes faith to believe that, Brandon.

00:07:12.992 --> 00:07:20.836
You grabbed onto a word that I gave you, and you embraced it.

00:07:20.836 --> 00:07:25.989
' Now, I don't look at anything that God says to me; I just believe it.

00:07:32.930 --> 00:07:33.280
I don't even realize it until He said it today when I was praying early this morning.

00:07:35.474 --> 00:07:44.114
He said, 'You grabbed onto it, and you're receiving it by faith and you don't even realize it.

00:07:44.114 --> 00:07:53.154
' I'm fully persuaded once He says something to me of that magnitude and I see it like that, I know that it's coming to pass.

00:07:53.154 --> 00:07:57.874
But there's no fruit of it yet.

00:07:57.874 --> 00:08:11.006
But whenever He spoke this to us—this is over a year ago—He said to us that we're bringing liberation and He's going to bring a major revival to Iran.

00:08:14.213 --> 00:08:22.639
And there would be things that are underground and archaeological discoveries in the days ahead that will come up out of the ground that will shake the Muslim community.

00:08:22.639 --> 00:08:34.400
So I just grab ahold of it and it's just like Abraham; I'm fully persuaded that what He has promised, He is able also to perform.

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:38.373
When He said, 'You're going to have a million subscribers.

00:08:38.373 --> 00:08:42.609
I want you to have a million-man and woman prayer army.

00:08:42.609 --> 00:09:01.306
' Two years ago when we had a hundred subscribers or less—of course, everybody starts out with nothing other than the family members who were excited that you started a YouTube channel—and then they join on and say, 'Oh yeah, we're subscribed; we're watching, good luck'—and then you set out and you go, 'I'm going to do this.

00:09:01.306 --> 00:09:06.080
' And then look what happens—the Lord does it just like He said it.

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:09.149
And I just receive it by faith.

00:09:16.571 --> 00:09:16.823
I receive it just like when He said, 'Brandon, Megan will be completely healed.

00:09:16.823 --> 00:09:32.760
I'm going to restore that little girl, and she's going to come on the platforms that I've provided for you and she's going to be a testimony to the whole world that I'm still a Healer.

00:09:32.760 --> 00:09:35.439
' Have I seen the full manifestation of that?

00:09:35.439 --> 00:09:36.079
No.

00:09:36.079 --> 00:09:37.497
But I see fruit.

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:49.860
And whenever you see the first blossoms on the tree sometimes, then you may see the little bud with the little fruit on there, and you can see there's something there.

00:09:49.860 --> 00:09:56.160
But you're so far from tasting the full manifestation of it.

00:09:56.160 --> 00:10:06.515
All you have to do is just be patient and be giving God glory as you see the fruit ripen on the tree.

00:10:11.560 --> 00:10:11.810
It just takes time sometimes over the course of spring into summer to fall.

00:10:11.810 --> 00:10:17.111
Ripe apples come on the tree, and then in September, usually first of October, you get a really nice harvest of good apples.

00:10:20.840 --> 00:10:28.969
We had an old apple tree at our old house, and we used to get those apples and eat them.

00:10:30.461 --> 00:10:32.559
They were so good and so sweet, but it took forever.

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:40.272
And Paisley, my little girl, would walk out there and say, 'Daddy, is it ready yet in July?

00:10:40.272 --> 00:10:47.556
' And I said, 'No, if you eat it right now, it'll give you a bellyache because it's not ripe.

00:10:47.556 --> 00:10:52.983
' But we knew if we'd just be patient and keep watching it.

00:10:52.983 --> 00:11:09.536
Even the little birds would come and lay there on the branches and peck at them a little bit at the top; they would get the firstfruits usually.

00:11:10.527 --> 00:11:21.537
But we knew that if we were patient, in due season—and a lot of you are in your due season—people may not understand what you're going through.

00:11:21.537 --> 00:11:31.771
They may look at you and say, 'He's cranky,' 'She's cranky,' 'He has all this going on because of the pressure.

00:11:31.771 --> 00:11:38.251
' It's the pressure that causes the coal to transform into that beautiful diamond.

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:44.400
It takes pressure.

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:00.359
And sometimes pressure makes you uncomfortable.

00:12:00.359 --> 00:12:04.311
The fruit in the process of waiting for something sometimes makes you uncomfortable.

00:12:04.311 --> 00:12:19.250
But I'm trying to tell you, if you do not get weary in well-doing, do not get weary in well-doing, you will reap if you faint not.

00:12:29.439 --> 00:12:29.919
And I have seen it time and time again.

00:12:29.919 --> 00:12:37.539
If you are not weary in well-doing, you will reap the fruit of what you're believing for.

00:12:37.539 --> 00:12:49.270
If you just believe God and have that bulldog mentality and say, "God, I know I'm fully persuaded that what you have promised, you are able also to perform it.

00:12:49.270 --> 00:12:51.138
I am not letting go.

00:12:51.138 --> 00:12:54.000
I will not bow.

00:12:54.000 --> 00:12:58.180
I will not bend my knee to Baal.

00:12:58.180 --> 00:13:05.450
I will stand on the promises that you said that by your stripes Megan healed.

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:12.319
" And that's what you do and that's what you continue to do.

00:13:13.760 --> 00:13:17.760
And so if you have something in your life that seems to be impossible, God specializes in impossible situations.

00:13:17.760 --> 00:13:20.840
All things are possible to him who believes.

00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:28.251
So, I want to encourage you tonight to don't give up on what you're believing for.

00:13:28.251 --> 00:13:30.180
There's an expiration date to your problems.

00:13:30.180 --> 00:13:33.040
There's an expiration date to what you're looking at.

00:13:34.449 --> 00:13:39.229
And say, "Hey, I'm telling you, in the name of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, be thou removed.

00:13:39.229 --> 00:13:41.120
Be thou cast into the sea.

00:13:41.120 --> 00:13:46.171
I will not doubt in my heart, and I know I will have whatsoever things I say.

00:13:48.688 --> 00:13:53.360
" And I believe that this mountain is going to be removed in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:13:57.440 --> 00:13:58.366
And you just got to keep on keeping on.

00:13:58.366 --> 00:14:03.431
It's not one drop that makes the indention in those caves.

00:14:03.431 --> 00:14:10.389
It's thousands and millions of drops of water in that place consecutively that makes the indention inside of that rock.

00:14:10.389 --> 00:14:20.719
And you look at stalagmites and stalactites or whatever they call them, and you see the tubes and you say, "Well, how long did that take?

00:14:34.259 --> 00:14:34.639
" Well, that took millions of years or hundreds of thousands or whatever.

00:14:34.639 --> 00:14:38.240
It's the faith that doesn't give up on the ground.

00:14:38.240 --> 00:14:45.893
It's the seed, it's the oak tree, it's the little acorn that doesn't give up on that ground.

00:14:48.160 --> 00:14:55.376
And it's even like Billy was saying today at his thing, you can pluck out the little seeds, but you can't go down and pick up an oak tree anymore because why?

00:14:55.376 --> 00:14:58.930
It's grabbed a hold of that dirt and it has a foundation.

00:14:58.930 --> 00:15:01.149
Its taproots went too deep.

00:15:01.149 --> 00:15:16.069
So when your taproot goes way too deep and you get your foundation and those roots down in that soil, no matter how bad the winds of life try to blow you over, you know that oak tree is going to make it through the storm, especially a healthy one.

00:15:16.069 --> 00:15:22.059
But a little acorn that just has barely any kind of root on it, a bird can pluck it up.

00:15:22.059 --> 00:15:24.160
But it's the faith of a mustard seed.

00:15:24.160 --> 00:15:27.840
You've got to have the faith of a mustard seed.

00:15:27.840 --> 00:15:35.310
It just takes a little bit to make that big old tree, that big old bush.

00:15:49.400 --> 00:15:49.760
It doesn't take a lot.

00:15:49.760 --> 00:15:52.228
Well, "Brandon, you've got great faith.

00:15:52.228 --> 00:15:52.914
" No.

00:15:52.914 --> 00:15:57.400
Faith cometh by hearing and hearing by the word of God.

00:15:57.400 --> 00:16:01.120
How bad do you want your life circumstances to change?

00:16:03.851 --> 00:16:07.640
The same pants I put on just like you, one leg at a time.

00:16:13.428 --> 00:16:13.656
And you've got to keep on keeping on.

00:16:13.656 --> 00:16:15.074
I even have my days.

00:16:15.074 --> 00:16:17.573
I get down, but I shake it off.

00:16:30.462 --> 00:16:30.631
I shake it off.

00:16:32.240 --> 00:16:33.680
I say, "I'm not going to get down anymore.

00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:39.839
I'm going to pick myself up out of this ditch.

00:16:42.204 --> 00:16:44.480
" I pick Diana up out of the ditch.

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:47.954
Braden picks us up out of the ditch.

00:16:47.954 --> 00:16:52.240
Paisley preaches to us and picks us up.

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:56.039
We all know the ditch is there.

00:16:56.039 --> 00:17:02.000
Sometimes you fall into it, but you just pick yourself up, you brush yourself off, and you keep walking.

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:18.354
When people try to knock you in the ditch, sometimes even family try to knock you in the ditch, you just say, "Hey, no, I'm not going to allow this phone call, I'm not going to allow this to derail me even from doing this video today.

00:17:25.028 --> 00:17:25.382
" I have my obstacles.

00:17:27.343 --> 00:17:28.432
I have to keep myself strong.

00:17:28.432 --> 00:17:41.508
I am strong in the Lord and in the power of His might even whenever you wouldn't believe.

00:17:46.150 --> 00:17:46.559
And then people get so mad at me.

00:17:52.832 --> 00:17:53.248
They say, "Brandon, why do you talk about the haters?

00:18:07.829 --> 00:18:08.057
" You wouldn't believe the obstacles that I've come through this week.

00:18:08.057 --> 00:18:09.200
You wouldn't believe it.

00:18:09.872 --> 00:18:15.531
And I refuse to talk about the problem.

00:18:15.531 --> 00:18:23.079
I've tried so hard to refrain from talking about the haters and talking about the YouTubers.

00:18:34.799 --> 00:18:35.059
But you know what?

00:18:47.298 --> 00:18:47.582
I know that persecution comes for the word's sake.

00:19:02.559 --> 00:19:12.720
And whenever it's accurate and people see that there's fruit behind you, when you're starting to go up the mountain and they are down here and they've been down here for years, they always try to attack the people that are on top because they say, "How did they get there?

00:19:12.720 --> 00:19:25.029
" But it was one rock at a time, the vision: "I'm going to get to the top.

00:19:25.029 --> 00:19:32.046
I'm going to be with you, Jesus.

00:19:32.046 --> 00:19:36.495
I want to be closer to you.

00:19:36.495 --> 00:19:45.440
" One thing at a time, one day at a time, I choose to follow you.

00:19:46.880 --> 00:19:49.867
And I can't do this all on my own.

00:19:49.867 --> 00:19:56.256
It's like I was listening when Billy said today, Kathryn used to say all the time that God could use anybody other than her.

00:19:56.256 --> 00:20:00.560
God could have used all these people other than me.

00:20:06.213 --> 00:20:06.547
And that's exactly where I feel all the time.

00:20:06.547 --> 00:20:07.977
It's not Brandon Biggs.

00:20:19.140 --> 00:20:19.560
I am not able to see anything on my own.

00:20:42.720 --> 00:20:42.959
I'm not able to see in the future without Jesus.

00:21:06.679 --> 00:21:07.199
He shows me these things.

00:21:07.199 --> 00:21:13.360
I believe with all my heart because you can see it in the news a couple days later.

00:21:13.360 --> 00:21:15.360
Some people get mad.

00:21:28.200 --> 00:21:28.640
They say it's familiar spirits, but I know that it's Jesus because I feel His presence.

00:21:29.520 --> 00:21:32.194
And in His presence there's fullness of joy.

00:21:32.194 --> 00:21:34.457
In His presence there's fullness of peace.

00:21:37.759 --> 00:21:38.729
People may not understand your level that God's called you to, and they're not meant to.

00:21:38.729 --> 00:21:47.600
Usually, it's just those that are the closest ones, like Diana and my son and my daughter, and they understand.

00:21:47.600 --> 00:21:57.430
They've known the trial, they've known what we've been through, and they're the only ones that really matter.

00:21:58.980 --> 00:22:06.860
And sometimes it may just be that you're by yourself and you just keep walking through the mud and you'll get there.

00:22:06.860 --> 00:22:08.770
Keep on keeping on.

00:22:08.770 --> 00:22:12.440
Keep being obedient to the small things.

00:22:12.440 --> 00:22:20.390
It's not the great big things; that's the moment that happens every once in a while.

00:22:34.206 --> 00:22:34.571
It's the day-to-day, the mundane.

00:22:43.982 --> 00:22:44.311
What you do in the mundane will get you to the big event.

00:22:44.311 --> 00:22:50.480
But people want the big event, but they didn't get the day-to-day in the mundane.

00:22:53.840 --> 00:22:54.137
And I've learned this over the years.

00:22:54.137 --> 00:22:57.626
It's the janitor behind the toilet that cleans.

00:22:58.480 --> 00:23:03.899
And even I told the Lord if I had to go back to doing it again, that's where I found who I was.

00:23:03.899 --> 00:23:08.620
That's how I found who He was.

00:23:08.620 --> 00:23:11.049
It's the dying to self.

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:21.154
And most people just want the aha moments, but they don't want to do what it takes to get to the process to get there.

00:23:21.154 --> 00:23:22.933
And it's not easy.

00:23:22.933 --> 00:23:25.600
It costs a lot.

00:23:25.600 --> 00:23:34.640
And it's a lonely, lonely place because you don't let just everybody in your circle.

00:23:34.640 --> 00:23:36.491
It's a very lonely place.

00:23:49.856 --> 00:23:50.104
And I think that's a healthy place because He's in that place.

00:23:50.104 --> 00:23:51.096
It's not Kathryn.

00:23:51.096 --> 00:23:52.836
Billy always talks about how Kathryn was alone.

00:23:52.836 --> 00:23:57.039
She always talks about how she's alone.

00:24:13.009 --> 00:24:13.279
And I realize it is what she always says: "It cost me so much," and I get it more and more all the time.

00:24:13.279 --> 00:24:20.022
This is what He said to me this morning in the wee hours of this morning.

00:24:20.022 --> 00:24:26.933
He said to me, because I said, "Lord, where's the greater percentage of the glory?

00:24:26.933 --> 00:24:32.800
What do we look for for healings and demonstration?

00:24:32.800 --> 00:24:36.293
" He said, "Brandon, what I'm calling for right now is the whole man.

00:24:45.463 --> 00:24:45.725
" And He says, "You know a lot about deliverance because of what you've walked through.

00:24:53.496 --> 00:24:53.828
And I want not just physical healing, but in the soulish realm.

00:25:06.560 --> 00:25:06.880
" And I will call people to walk in healings, demonstrations, manifestations, and deliverance ministry so that you will cast out devils in my name.

00:25:13.529 --> 00:25:15.200
And he said, "I'm bringing a special anointing for casting out devils on certain individual ministries.

00:25:15.200 --> 00:25:18.880
I'm looking for the bride without spot or wrinkle.

00:25:24.354 --> 00:25:24.869
The spot and the wrinkle are sin and demonic oppression.

00:25:27.440 --> 00:25:42.007
" And he said, "I'm looking for people to be completely free from the top of their head to the soles of their feet, Brandon.

00:25:49.039 --> 00:25:50.780
" And there are so many people that have deviated off of deliverance ministry.

00:25:50.780 --> 00:25:53.010
It's gotten flaky over the years.

00:25:53.010 --> 00:25:58.499
And people have seen those who have grabbed onto it, they get flaky.

00:25:58.889 --> 00:26:01.931
I heard Billy talking about how people have buckets for vomit.

00:26:01.931 --> 00:26:04.960
Brother Hagin used to talk about this too.

00:26:04.960 --> 00:26:16.781
People had sacks and they'd bring them to church all the time because they were vomiting these devils up.

00:26:16.781 --> 00:26:18.346
Now, I have seen this happen.

00:26:26.080 --> 00:26:26.320
And it was through me when Jesus set me free.

00:26:26.320 --> 00:26:29.391
