He's talking to Braden.

01:21:18.639 --> 01:21:19.699
He's talking to Diana.

01:21:19.699 --> 01:21:21.199
He's talking to my daughters.

01:21:21.199 --> 01:21:22.228
He's talking to me.

01:21:22.228 --> 01:21:23.760
He's talking to my family.

01:21:23.760 --> 01:21:24.880
This is personal.

01:21:24.880 --> 01:21:30.560
This isn't some book that I'm just reading that sounds good.

01:21:30.560 --> 01:21:31.903
No, it's personal.

01:21:31.903 --> 01:21:36.100
Do you think it'll happen for me?

01:21:36.100 --> 01:21:39.691
No, not if you just think it; I know it.

01:21:39.691 --> 01:21:40.709
I'm fully persuaded.

01:21:40.709 --> 01:21:42.390
'Well, what if you die, Brandon?

01:21:42.390 --> 01:21:45.840
' Well, then I go to be with the Lord.

01:22:06.480 --> 01:22:07.160
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

01:22:56.719 --> 01:22:57.542
I still win.

01:23:02.480 --> 01:23:06.600
I say this just out of love and compassion for you all.

01:23:06.600 --> 01:23:26.297
If you don't understand the word of God and it's not rooted and grounded in your heart, the enemy comes in to kill, steal, and destroy.

01:23:26.297 --> 01:23:32.447
And he cannot devour.

01:23:35.440 --> 01:23:51.040
The Bible says he comes as a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

01:23:58.663 --> 01:23:59.920
He's looking for the ones he can devour.

01:23:59.920 --> 01:24:12.149
What makes him not devour you?

01:24:12.159 --> 01:24:28.624
As a roaring lion, he doesn't devour the ones that know and make this personal.

01:24:28.624 --> 01:24:41.440
It's not just a Bible verse; this is life's blood.

01:24:41.440 --> 01:24:44.370
This is my heartbeat—not in the natural, but in the spiritual.

01:24:58.399 --> 01:24:58.639
And when you get a revelation of it in the spiritual first, it radiates to the natural.

01:24:58.639 --> 01:24:59.840
Same with Psalm 23.

01:25:13.510 --> 01:25:13.900
I won't take the time to do that because I'm already over an hour.

01:25:13.900 --> 01:25:15.459
Maybe next time.

01:25:15.459 --> 01:25:20.995
But do it the same way.

01:25:24.760 --> 01:25:25.120
The Lord is my shepherd; I shall not want.

01:25:25.120 --> 01:25:30.366
He makes me lie down in green pastures; he leads me beside the still waters.

01:25:30.366 --> 01:25:31.463
That's me.

01:25:31.463 --> 01:25:34.342
So I want you to do that.

01:25:34.342 --> 01:25:35.840
Mirror it.

01:25:35.840 --> 01:25:36.320
Put yourself in it.

01:25:36.320 --> 01:25:38.538
Visualize yourself.

01:25:38.538 --> 01:25:47.720
Put it inside your mind.

01:25:50.317 --> 01:25:56.071
I see Susie, Bobby, Jeff, Joe—whatever your name is—I see me as this.

01:27:16.239 --> 01:27:16.519
And don't just do it once.

01:27:16.519 --> 01:27:29.383
Do it over and over until it becomes so real to you that there's not a devil in hell that can talk you out of it.

01:27:29.383 --> 01:27:35.387
Faith comes by hearing and hearing by the word of God.

01:27:35.387 --> 01:27:36.453
Not having heard.

01:29:19.280 --> 01:29:19.813
It means you hear it over and over again.

01:29:19.813 --> 01:29:27.160
How do you believe you're saved?

01:29:27.160 --> 01:29:32.099
By grace, I'm saved by faith.

01:29:34.863 --> 01:29:35.455
I receive my deliverance by faith.

01:29:38.919 --> 01:30:20.823
I receive my salvation and I'm saved because Jesus said if we confess our sins, he is faithful and just to forgive us of our sins and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

01:30:20.823 --> 01:30:26.729
I receive it by faith.

01:30:26.729 --> 01:30:51.795
If you realize how big of a miracle it truly is to say, 'I was once lost, but now I'm found.

01:30:51.795 --> 01:31:53.058
I was blind, but now I see,' you wouldn't take it so lightly.

01:31:53.058 --> 01:33:22.760
It truly is a bigger miracle than any kind of creative miracle that you could ever comprehend.

01:33:22.760 --> 01:33:26.833
To be lost, but now found.

01:33:26.833 --> 01:33:30.978
To be blind, but now I see.

01:33:30.978 --> 01:33:32.743
He saved me.

01:33:32.743 --> 01:33:34.389
He delivered me.

01:33:34.389 --> 01:33:43.840
He turned my life around.

01:34:17.627 --> 01:34:31.519
And it was by his grace, by his love that he said, 'I gave my life for you.

01:34:31.519 --> 01:34:38.507
' And people just flippantly say, 'Oh, yeah, I'm saved by grace.

01:34:38.507 --> 01:34:39.493
' No.

01:34:56.990 --> 01:34:57.420
I was once blind, but now I see.

01:34:57.420 --> 01:35:31.460
So when you hear of Nipah and you hear all these things, the very first thing you should do—instead of what that lady yells—you get this down inside of you even more because I tried to tell you what they're going to try to do in the days ahead.

01:35:31.460 --> 01:35:46.870
Can we have authority?

