01:37:06.320 --> 01:37:22.560
So when it ministers to you and you feel like there's some fruit to it, then eat it.

01:37:22.560 --> 01:37:31.749
If not, then put it on a shelf.

01:37:31.749 --> 01:37:35.480
But I'm going to stand by this.

01:37:35.480 --> 01:38:20.340
As for me and my house, we're going to serve the Lord.

01:38:20.340 --> 01:38:43.504
Father, we just thank you, Lord.

01:38:43.504 --> 01:39:10.420
We're so grateful that you give us the Bible to look at and to read and to make it a part of us.

01:39:10.420 --> 01:39:15.040
We breathe it in.

01:39:15.040 --> 01:39:21.840
We breathe in the refreshing of who you are to us.

01:40:13.180 --> 01:40:13.610
We were once lost, but now we're found.

01:40:13.610 --> 01:40:17.520
I was blind, but now I see.

01:40:17.520 --> 01:40:28.782
I'm not moved by what I see or what I feel; I'm moved by what the word of God says.

01:40:28.782 --> 01:40:31.453
'Brandon, you've got issues.

01:40:31.453 --> 01:40:36.620
' Yes, we all have issues.

01:40:36.620 --> 01:40:38.719
We're a work in progress.

01:40:38.719 --> 01:40:43.580
People tick me off all the time.

01:41:06.720 --> 01:41:07.040
You have to say, 'Hey God, I walk in love.

01:41:07.040 --> 01:41:18.346
' Even when you get off the phone and you're so upset after a conversation, 'Oh God, forgive me.

01:41:27.680 --> 01:41:28.000
I walk in love.

01:41:28.000 --> 01:41:30.360
Help me to come up higher.

01:41:30.360 --> 01:41:32.840
' I receive it by grace.

01:42:17.359 --> 01:42:17.599
Father, Christ in me, the hope of glory.

01:42:17.599 --> 01:42:42.730
If you're here tonight and you've never asked Jesus Christ to be your Lord, before I go any further, if you're saying, 'Brandon, I'm not even born again or I'm backsliding,' and what you just said really touched my heart or made me second-guess myself...

01:42:42.730 --> 01:42:44.159
should I know him?

01:42:44.159 --> 01:42:47.531
Yes, you're running out of time.

01:42:55.497 --> 01:43:08.655
In Acts chapter 2, it talks about how the Holy Spirit pricked the hearts of even the hardest of the people.

01:43:25.679 --> 01:43:26.019
