01:48:28.045 --> 01:48:28.423
You may be here and you're backsliding, and you're not all in anymore.

01:48:28.423 --> 01:48:31.289
You're not all on fire for Jesus.

01:48:31.289 --> 01:48:35.502
Your heart has become so cold because you became weary in well-doing.

01:48:36.213 --> 01:49:00.620
And all the people around you that you've been hanging out with, they've been a bad influence on you, and they're talking you out of your personal relationship with Jesus Christ—all that religious stuff, we don't want to do all that, whatever.

01:49:01.320 --> 01:49:05.920
And over the course of time, your heart has become callous.

01:49:18.1000 --> 01:49:23.862
The Holy Spirit warns you time and time again, "Don't hang around them.

01:49:23.862 --> 01:49:25.690
" "Oh, it's okay.

01:49:25.690 --> 01:49:32.410
I can witness to them and be a light as I hang around them.

01:49:32.410 --> 01:49:39.090
I'm going to be a light in the darkness tonight as we go to the bar.

01:49:39.090 --> 01:49:49.390
" But over the course of time, that water drip brought you back underneath them because you didn't remain underneath the Word of God.

