01:49:52.582 --> 01:50:06.663
You started hanging out with the world all the time, going out doing things that you knew were wrong in the first place.

01:50:10.239 --> 01:50:16.160
And now you're looking at yourself, and you've got chains of iron all around you.

01:50:16.160 --> 01:50:21.976
And you're thinking, "What happened to my life?

01:50:21.976 --> 01:50:31.360
" It was one bad choice that brought me here, and it was repeated.

01:50:31.360 --> 01:50:40.832
But tonight, God wants to set you free.

01:50:40.832 --> 01:50:49.394
He's never left you, and He's never forsaken you.

01:50:49.394 --> 01:50:55.840
He's an ever-present help in a time of need.

01:50:56.080 --> 01:51:12.470
