02:02:53.600 --> 02:03:26.950
I thank you, Lord, that from this day forward, I'll be with you in paradise.

02:03:26.960 --> 02:03:47.714
Thank you, Lord, that I'm born again.

02:03:47.714 --> 02:04:17.102
