02:04:17.102 --> 02:04:56.873
And as far as the east is from the west, you've taken my sins from me.

02:05:51.570 --> 02:05:51.920
And tonight's my night for a brand new start as I give my heart over to you.

02:05:51.920 --> 02:06:21.910
Thank you, Jesus.

02:06:21.920 --> 02:06:23.680
Amen and amen.

02:06:23.680 --> 02:06:33.333
" Well, I believe if you just said that prayer, you just asked Jesus Christ to be your Lord and personal Savior.

02:06:36.079 --> 02:06:44.240
